data.title: Great for price
data.body: I recently purchased the 5oz Cupcake Pans, and overall, I'm satisfied with my purchase. The aluminum foil cupcake liners with lids are a convenient addition, making it easy to store or transport baked goods. The square brownie mini cake baking pans are sturdy, and the red color adds a festive touch. The cupcake cups muffin tin holders are easy to use and eliminate the need for cleanup. However, the lids could be a bit more secure, as I noticed some minor leaks. Despite this, the product serves its purpose well for casual baking needs.
